OXISIX is a dynamic and environmentally friendly company offering professional services, serving the greater Simcoe County and more. We are a local, family owned & operated company, that provides you with personalized, quality service at affordable prices.

profile: For the last 18 years, The Critter Guy – Wildlife and Pest Control has been providing quality pest control in Grey Bruce and Huron Counties. With a great amount of experience and a price that’s right – we will get your wildlife problem under control when it comes to animal removal from your home or business property. From squirrels, bats, raccoons, skunks, and even dead animals… The Critter Guy is your one-stop-shop solution for animal removal services that gets it done, WITHOUT overcomplicating it!
